Package: stringshaper
Title: Bindings to the HarfBuzz library for Text Shaping
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Thomas Lin", "Pedersen", , "thomas.pedersen@rstudio.com", c("cre", "aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5147-4711")),
    person("RStudio", role = "cph")
    )
Description: Provides access to the text shaping functionality in the HarfBuzz
    library. 'stringshaper' is a low-level utility package mainly for graphic 
    devices that expands upon the font toolset provided by the 'systemfonts'
    package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
